data.title: 5.4.1f Additional Information Alumni Association
data.meta_description: 5.4.1f-Additional-Information-Alumni-Association - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document discusses the Alumni Association of MGM Institute of Health Sciences. It was established in 2014 and aims to foster collaboration between alumni and current students/faculty. The association has 7 chapters across different constituent colleges. It works to support the Institute's academic and research activities through alumni engagement activities, guest lectures, mentorship programs and endowment sponsorship. The association leadership structure and past contributions of alumni are outlined.
